              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <blockquote class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
                "Guido gave an excellent presentation at our event. His knowledge and expertise in the field of CRO was evident throughout his talk. The audience was engaged and provided positive feedback."
              </blockquote>
